<li><i>The Sacred Plants of our Ancestors</i> by <a href="/wiki/Christian_R%C3%A4tsch" title="Christian Rätsch">Christian Rätsch</a>, published in <a href="/wiki/Tyr_(journal)#Volume_2" title="Tyr (journal)">TYR: Myth—Culture—Tradition Vol. 2</a>, 2003–2004 - <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0972029214" class="internal">ISBN 0-9720292-1-4</a></li>
<li>Jackson, Simon (2007). ' 'Cannabis &amp; Meditation - An Explorer's Guide'. Headstuff Books. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780955385315" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-9553853-1-5</a> . Second Edition (2009) <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780955385346" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-9553853-4-6</a></li>
